data.description: Location, location, location! Located on a quiet street minutes from Hartsfield Jackson International Airport, Delta, the Porsche plant, Tyler Perry Studios, the colorful shops and restaurants of downtown Hapeville, several parks and rec centers, and the anticipated future East Point Commons development. Easy access to MARTA and all major highways. Recently fully renovated (2020) including windows, floors, counters, electric, plumbing and appliances. Clean and bright interior features modern touches. Master bedroom with ensuite bathroom featuring extra large glass shower. Cook dinner in the gourmet kitchen or step out onto the back porch to grill with friends. Move in ready! Don't let current interest rates keep you from this home: Special financing is available for this property through Guaranteed Rate Affinity, including below-market interest rate or No Money Down. On top of that, Seller is willing to finance a 2/1 buydown that can lower the Buyer's interest rate by 2% for the first 12 months and 1% for months 13-24, saving THOUSANDS of dollars!"
